### Overview

To enable use `autoheight: true`. At the moment works only with 1 item on screen.
The plan is to calculate all visible items and change height according to heightest item.

```
//default settings:
Autoheight.Defaults = {
	autoheight: false,
	autoheightClass: 'owl-height'
};
```


### Setup
```
$('.owl-carousel').owlCarousel({
	items:1,
	margin:10,
	autoheight:true
});

```

